世界带来了欢笑，其公益精神令人钦佩。如果你错过了这个故事，我会总结一下。上周，谷歌发布了 Gemini，这是一款人工智能聊天机器人和图像生成器，旨在与 Open AI 和其他公司的类似应用程序竞争。这是一次非常重要的发布，但它也犯了最严重的错误。</p><p>人们一开始玩它，就注意到了一些奇怪的事情。当他们要求它提供历史人物的照片时，无论背景如何，它都会提供“多样化”的图像。当它被要求提供维京人（历史上最白的人）的图像时，发生了以下情况： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5a866262-96ec-45dd-9c62-1532681cb2a7_480x288.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5a866262-96ec-45dd-9c62-1532681cb2a7_480x288.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5a866262-96ec-45dd-9c62-1532681cb2a7_480x288.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5a866262-96ec-45dd-9c62-1532681cb2a7_480x288.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5a866262-96ec-45dd-9c62-1532681cb2a7_480x288.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5a866262-96ec-45dd-9c62-1532681cb2a7_480x288.jpeg" width="354" height="212.4" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5a866262-96ec-45dd-9c62-1532681cb2a7_480x288.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&q